{"tid":1160323,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"考試出貓係lecture屌到個professor喊","createTime":"2019-05-18T11:41:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T00:22:10.000Z","uid":158407,"like":22,"dislike":128,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d99b7192f3e6fc8460cd3b9bb1959190adc2c664","tid":1160323,"uid":158407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T11:41:16.000Z","msg":"岩岩finals係prepare過，入到lecture就知出事了。<br />\n即刻攞咗部手機出嚟，點知考到一半比個professor周到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我即刻大大聲屌番佢老母<br />\n<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nprofessor：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nprofessor：你做咩出貓呀？<br />\n我：屌你老母，你唔撚問你自己點解教到咁撚閪？<br />\nprofessor：你講咩呀？<br />\n我：話你教畜呀，廢柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後d學生開始起哄，拍晒手咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲見到個大波女神勁撚淫出晒水咁望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後因為場面太混亂，個教畜同全部人道晒歉話人人有A range<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n臨走前幾條女圍住我話好想幫我含，而家帶住3條女去緊維記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樓主好波<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />教畜死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ccb42eaa63f0e771cc17694797e19e40bc1a766","tid":1160323,"uid":38904,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T11:42:20.000Z","msg":"讀書太大壓力驚要retake?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dda588cf531f5868ce8b636a273ff4595665b8b","tid":1160323,"uid":29080,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2